Basic installation
    cp shiva /usr/local/bin/
    cp shiva.conf /usr/local/etc/
    cp shiva.list /usr/local/etc/
    mkdir /usr/local/etc/shiva/

Create custom lists of servers
    /usr/local/etc/shiva/custom_list

Add lines

    server1.example.com
    server2.example.com
    server3.example.com

View lists
    shiva -l
    custom_list

